Error in function (type, msg, asError = TRUE)  :
  Failed to connect to ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov port 21: Connection refused

Maybe seqlevelsStyle should check if the genome of a GRanges object has been set and throw an informative error?

With kind regards,
Freek Manders

